<h2>Who was Jordan Nagler?</h2>

<p>Jordan Nagler joined the ISE family in 2001.  After graduating from Idaho State University, Jordan moved to New York to pursue his degree in Finance.  After meeting Wayne Brewer on the golf course, he came to ISE.  It quickly became obvious of his strength in the field and he became the Executive Director of International Student Exchange in  2003 and held that position until his untimely passing in October of 2008. Durring those years, he helped grow and strengthen the ISE family and the exchange industry as well.  </p>
 
